==Notes==
*This is an underwater zone. It features all the restrictions and special mechanics of [[underwater adventuring]].  Amongst other things, this means this zone has a <font color=red>-100%</font> penalty to [[Meat from Monsters|meat drops]] and [[Items from Monsters|item drops]].

==References==
*This zone is a reference to [[Wikipedia:SS Edmund Fitzgerald|SS Edmund Fitzgerald]] a freighter on the Great Lakes that sunk suddenly during a storm in 1975. The ship's story was popularized in [[Wikipedia:Gordon Lightfoot|Gordon Lightfoot]]'s song "[[Wikipedia:The Wreck of the Edmund Fitzgerald|The Wreck of the Edmund Fitzgerald]]".
